{"tid":1943823,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"水晶姥姥奶洋腸奶到傻撚左？走去撐feather and bone","createTime":"2020-03-26T04:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T05:08:58.000Z","uid":122208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f503b0d48305c76800bbaf5fb7b15f8a9b5e86d6","tid":1943823,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:01:35.000Z","msg":"總之對家做乜都係錯，黃議員做街站，附近係feather and bone, feather and bone個鬼佬老闆驚影響生意，無警告之下去撕爛區議員海報<br />\n<br />\n水晶姥姥居然叫議員企過少少解決事件，佢係咪奶洋腸盲反泛民搞到傻撚左，仲要約人去feather and bone聚餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMjRSuw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMjRSuw.png&h=25dd6081&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LyfzHS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LyfzHS.png&h=67c79621&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ba30aa5c1136c46a7d54d380e3a4be1914d7fb1","tid":1943823,"uid":331949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"who？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfa2eKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnfa2eKd.jpg&h=40b745e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d870dce72260d8e8e9e849d73372cf109452a02","tid":1943823,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba30aa5c1136c46a7d54d380e3a4be1914d7fb1","tid":1943823,"uid":331949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"who？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfa2eKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnfa2eKd.jpg&h=40b745e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:56:21.000Z","msg":"白咭佬陳雲d傻粉，聽白咭佬賣樓既傻閪"},{"pid":"55e9d80cf96e2ec5918bf2d1ec976cd37a02c218","tid":1943823,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d870dce72260d8e8e9e849d73372cf109452a02","tid":1943823,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba30aa5c1136c46a7d54d380e3a4be1914d